column5: Art ,Pops,GCD and I arrived in Virginia safe and sound.Dawg still has 12 hrs ahead of him tomorrow.Was a great GTG,I seem to only have pics of Rich and Spiels dogs. Joe
Wow !!!...You made good time...Glad to hear your home safe and sound...
Once again work got in the way of me having fun with the gang. Glad to hear that you are all safe and everyone seemed to have a good time!
Hmmm... Im glad you guys made it safe... by the way... has anyone seen my shirt????
Glad you made it home safe, guess you didn't follow any shortcuts  Maureen
Glad to hear you had a good time and was able to get back home safe and sound.  I'll warn the state patrol about the dawg
RRRRRRRRRRRRRRole TIDE! for Dog  Nice to meet you guys. Cool boats by the way.
Youse guys are the highlight of the party.  Great to see Dawg and the Plummas, and Pops, too.  Glad that you're home s & s.
Glad to hear you got home safely!  Anyone hear from Glen yet?
I haven't heard anything yet.He was picking up his pup in Atlanta this evening and heading home.He'll prolly check in shortly. Joe
Forget about your shirt TJ....you should be asking where your pants are.....
....Glad to see y'all made it home.  You guys is sump'n, dang it's just that it's all over too quick.
